  • Conclusions

Introduction¶

Forbes is a global media company, focusing on business, investing, technology, entrepreneurship, leadership, and lifestyle, and They have a section for billionaires ,it contains 2755 billionaires from all world , so We will analyze this data to answer the following questions.

  1. The total number of billions owned by billionaires?
  2. The richest man in the world and top 10?
  3. The billionaires are the least wealthy?
  4. A country with more billionaires?
  5. Countries that contribute the most to the total value?
  6. Which industries do billionaires invest in most?
  7. industries that contribute the most to the total value?
  8. what is the relationship between age and networth?
  9. further analysis on middle eaast!
